{"tid":1030511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛州女子求歡不遂　痛毆未婚夫被捕","createTime":"2019-02-21T04:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T11:21:24.000Z","uid":225846,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bca6e021ae8329fb56eec1a6e499e904d40a8c95","tid":1030511,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220190919117-0220_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190220193544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220190919117-0220_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190220193544&h=d20f8c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埃爾南德斯（左圖及右圖左）疑求歡不遂，憤而痛毆特斯代爾（右圖右）。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n美國佛羅里達州一名21歲女子，周一（18日）疑因求歡不遂，憤而痛毆未婚夫，並扯開男方的衣服，後者嚇得報警求助。警方到場發現女子一絲不掛，而且非常激動，女方其後更襲警。她最終被控兩項襲擊罪，准以6000美元（約4.7萬港元）保釋外出。 <br />\n<br />\n報道指，女子埃爾南德斯（Samantha Jewel Hernandez）與未婚夫特斯代爾（Lucas Truesdale）同居。事發當日早上，埃爾南德斯在住所向特斯代爾求歡，惟遭男方拒絕，遂對男方施襲，痛打對方的頭部。 <br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，發現特斯代爾的臉及頸出現抓痕，上衣亦被撕破。埃爾南德斯被捕時聲稱自己太醉，無法接受問話。不過，她被帶上警車後，曾一度假裝昏迷，又向警員吐口水。法官禁止她與未婚夫接觸，案件將於4月12日提堂。據悉，埃爾南德斯去年8月曾因行為不檢被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220190919117-0220_00972_001_02p.jpg?20190220193544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220190919117-0220_00972_001_02p.jpg%3F20190220193544&h=8a11255a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃爾南德斯被控襲擊罪。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等我代勞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ada9beb3de5027a460995e98fbe20defa4cf45","tid":1030511,"uid":45213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"mugshot仲靚過生活照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f903d6c6d49354d6b30dd0ff0e7fe5cbf54a49d9","tid":1030511,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:33:20.000Z","msg":"正面普通，側面好正"},{"pid":"05e0b70aa19528e864d51dc02d665c87cea71f04","tid":1030511,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"你唔屌等我來呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4f2f4f47b13c16ecc50672e1111ed88176c621","tid":1030511,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qazQyNB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqazQyNB.jpg&h=f1423d16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db4c7823c643fea9925604b25b3ce2848e1c22fc","tid":1030511,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"我願意同佢交歡"},{"pid":"30e5e6563e0dc52e7087cc1658c845c676cecf0b","tid":1030511,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"9dcbb3f358189416e2b8223b11e106586016c54e","tid":1030511,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.sebastiandaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/samantha-jewel-hernandez-vero-beach-600x381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sebastiandaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fsamantha-jewel-hernandez-vero-beach-600x381.jpg&h=7c0954ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}